title: Underground Hip Hop Mega Pack
description:
Cage (Movies For The Blind), Jedi Mind Tricks (Violent By Design), Leak Brothers (Waterworld), Necro (Brutality Part 1), Atmosphere (Seven&#039;s Travels), Cannibal Ox (The Cold Vein), Vast Aire (Look Mom No Hands), Rhythm Ruckus (Futurecrimes). 

All fans of any of these eclectic group of artists should give Rhythm Ruckus A serious listen. Futurecrimes is a sonic amusement ride through the depravity of modern day America.
